#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:2
msgid "文件上传"
msgstr "File Upload"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:5
msgid "文件类型检测绕过"
msgstr "File Type Detection Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:8
msgid "更改请求绕过"
msgstr "Request Modification Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:9
msgid ""
"有的站点仅仅在前端检测了文件类型，这种类型的检测可以直接修改网络请求绕过。 同样的，有的站点在后端仅检查了HTTP Header中的信息，比如 "
"``Content-Type`` 等，这种检查同样可以通过修改网络请求绕过。"
msgstr ""
"Some sites only check file type on the frontend; this kind of check can be "
"bypassed by directly modifying the network request. Similarly, some sites "
"only check HTTP header information on the backend, such as ``Content-Type``;"
" those checks can also be bypassed by modifying the network request."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:13
msgid "Magic检测绕过"
msgstr "Magic Number Check Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:14
msgid "有的站点使用文件头来检测文件类型，这种检查可以在Shell前加入对应的字节以绕过检查。几种常见的文件类型的头字节如下表所示"
msgstr ""
"Some sites use file headers to detect file type. This check can be bypassed "
"by adding the corresponding bytes before the shell. Header bytes for several"
" common file types are shown below."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:17
msgid "类型"
msgstr "Type"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:17
msgid "二进制值"
msgstr "Binary Value"

