#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:27
msgid "后缀绕过"
msgstr "Extension Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:28
msgid "部分服务仅根据后缀、上传时的信息或Magic Header来判断文件类型，此时可以绕过。"
msgstr ""
"Some services determine file type only from the extension, upload metadata, "
"or Magic Header, which can be bypassed."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:30
msgid ""
"php由于历史原因，部分解释器可能支持符合正则 ``/ph(p[2-7]?|t(ml)?)/`` 的后缀，如 ``php`` / ``php5`` / "
"``pht`` / ``phtml`` / ``shtml`` / ``pwml`` / ``phtm`` 等 可在禁止上传php文件时测试该类型。"
msgstr ""
"For historical reasons, some PHP interpreters may support extensions that "
"match the regex ``/ph(p[2-7]?|t(ml)?)/``, such as ``php`` / ``php5`` / "
"``pht`` / ``phtml`` / ``shtml`` / ``pwml`` / ``phtm``. These can be tested "
"when PHP file uploads are blocked."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:32
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"jsp引擎则可能会解析 ``jspx`` / ``jspf`` / ``jspa`` / ``jsw`` / ``jsv`` / ``jtml`` "
"等后缀，asp支持 ``asa`` / ``asax`` / ``cer`` / ``cdx`` / ``aspx`` / ``ascx`` / "
"``ashx`` / ``asmx`` / ``asp{80-90}`` 等后缀。"
msgstr ""
"JSP engines may parse extensions such as ``jspx`` / ``jspf`` / ``jspa`` / "
"``jsw`` / ``jsv`` / ``jtml``. ASP supports extensions such as ``asa`` / "
"``asax`` / ``cer`` / ``cdx`` / ``aspx`` / ``ascx`` / ``ashx`` / ``asmx`` / "
"``asp{80-90}``."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:34
msgid ""
"除了这些绕过，其他的后缀同样可能带来问题，如 ``vbs`` / ``asis`` / ``sh`` / ``reg`` / ``cgi`` / "
"``exe`` / ``dll`` / ``com`` / ``bat`` / ``pl`` / ``cfc`` / ``cfm`` / ``ini``"
" 等。"
msgstr ""
"Beyond these bypasses, other extensions may also cause problems, such as "
"``vbs`` / ``asis`` / ``sh`` / ``reg`` / ``cgi`` / ``exe`` / ``dll`` / "
"``com`` / ``bat`` / ``pl`` / ``cfc`` / ``cfm`` / ``ini``."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:37
msgid "系统命名绕过"
msgstr "System Naming Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:38
msgid ""
"在Windows系统中，上传 ``index.php.`` 会重命名为 ``.`` ，可以绕过后缀检查。 也可尝试 ``index.php%20`` ，"
" ``index.php:1.jpg`` ``index.php::$DATA`` 等。 在Linux系统中，可以尝试上传名为 "
"``index.php/.`` 或 ``./aa/../index.php/.`` 的文件"
msgstr ""
"On Windows, uploading ``index.php.`` will be renamed by trimming the "
"trailing ``.``, which can bypass extension checks. You can also try "
"``index.php%20``, ``index.php:1.jpg``, ``index.php::$DATA``, and similar "
"names. On Linux, try uploading files named ``index.php/.`` or "
"``./aa/../index.php/.``."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:43
msgid ".user.ini"
msgstr ".user.ini"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:44
msgid ""
"在php执行的过程中，除了主 ``php.ini`` 之外，PHP 还会在每个目录下扫描 INI 文件，从被执行的 PHP 文件所在目录开始一直上升到 "
"web 根目录（$_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] 所指定的）。如果被执行的 PHP 文件在 web 根目录之外，则只扫描该目录。 "
"``.user.ini`` 中可以定义除了PHP_INI_SYSTEM以外的模式的选项，故可以使用 ``.user.ini`` "
"加上非php后缀的文件构造一个shell，比如 ``auto_prepend_file=01.gif`` 。"
msgstr ""
"During PHP execution, in addition to the main ``php.ini``, PHP scans INI "
"files in each directory, starting from the directory of the executed PHP "
"file up to the web root specified by ``$_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT']``. If the "
"executed PHP file is outside the web root, only that directory is scanned. "
"Options other than ``PHP_INI_SYSTEM`` mode can be defined in ``.user.ini``, "
"so ``.user.ini`` plus a non-PHP extension file can be used to construct a "
"shell, for example ``auto_prepend_file=01.gif``."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:47
msgid "WAF绕过"
msgstr "WAF Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:48
msgid "有的waf在编写过程中考虑到性能原因，只处理一部分数据，这时可以通过加入大量垃圾数据来绕过其处理函数。"
msgstr ""
"Some WAFs process only part of the data for performance reasons. In that "
"case, adding a large amount of junk data may bypass their processing logic."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:50
msgid "另外，Waf和Web系统对 ``boundary`` 的处理不一致，可以使用错误的 ``boundary`` 来完成绕过。"
msgstr ""
"In addition, when the WAF and web system handle ``boundary`` differently, an"
" incorrect ``boundary`` can be used to bypass checks."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:53
msgid "竞争上传绕过"
msgstr "Race Condition Upload Bypass"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:54
msgid "有的服务器采用了先保存，再删除不合法文件的方式，在这种服务器中，可以反复上传一个会生成Web Shell的文件并尝试访问，多次之后即可获得Shell。"
msgstr ""
"Some servers save uploaded files first and delete illegal files afterward. "
"On such servers, repeatedly uploading a file that generates a web shell and "
"trying to access it may eventually obtain a shell."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:57
msgid "攻击技巧"
msgstr "Attack Techniques"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:60
msgid "Apache重写GetShell"
msgstr "Apache Rewrite GetShell"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:61
msgid "Apache可根据是否允许重定向考虑上传.htaccess"
msgstr ""
"For Apache, consider uploading ``.htaccess`` depending on whether redirects "
"are allowed."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:63
msgid "内容为"
msgstr "With content:"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:70
msgid "就可以用png或者其他后缀的文件做php脚本了"
msgstr "This allows files with ``png`` or other extensions to be used as PHP scripts."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:73
msgid "软链接任意读文件"
msgstr "Arbitrary File Read via Symlink"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:74
msgid "上传的压缩包文件会被解压的文件时，可以考虑上传含符号链接的文件 若服务器没有做好防护，可实现任意文件读取的效果"
msgstr ""
"When uploaded archive files are extracted, consider uploading files that "
"contain symbolic links. If the server lacks proper protection, this can "
"enable arbitrary file reads."

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:78
msgid "防护技巧"
msgstr "Protection Tips"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:79
msgid "使用白名单限制上传文件的类型"
msgstr "Use a whitelist to restrict upload file types"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:80
msgid "使用更严格的文件类型检查方式"
msgstr "Use stricter file type checks"

#: ../../source/vuln/fileupload.rst:81
msgid "限制Web Server对上传文件夹的解析"
msgstr "Restrict the web server from parsing files in upload directories"

